      <title>贝莱德的科斯特里奇表示，盈利驱动的市场惩罚公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-09/earnings-driven-market-punishing-companies-says-blackrock-s-koesterich</link>
