    <item>
      <title>英国富时 100 指数在欧洲表现优于欧洲大盘，因英国央行加大降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/earnings-keep-european-stocks-near-record-highs-ahead-of-boe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国富时 100 指数表现优于欧洲指数，因为英国央行的最新政策决定推动了人们对降息的押注。企业盈利好坏参半，导致整体市场情绪低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/earnings-keep-european-stocks-near-record-highs-ahead-of-boe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 07:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
